## Summary

Ubermench: AI Business Assistant for trades workers in Mexico via WhatsApp. Bot name: **Chalán**.

**Stack:** NestJS + PostgreSQL + Prisma + Redis + BullMQ (backend), Next.js (web). Deployed on Railway.

**3 repos:** `~/ubermench/` (code), `~/ubermench-docs/` (docs), `~/ubermench-strategy/` (strategy).

**Key modules:** `ai/` (OpenAI function calling, tools in `ai.tools.ts`), `workspace/` (provider profile, cache-first), `income/`, `expense/` (puntual + recurring), `appointments/` (CRUD + timezone-aware), `whatsapp/` (webhook, dedup via setNX), `reminders/`, `contacts/` (CRM), `payments/` (Stripe Connect Express).

**Current focus:** see "Foco actual" in `.sanctuary/project-context.md` (updated on every roadmap rewrite).

**Design decisions:** Intent classification via function calling (not prompt rules). All dates timezone-aware. Sanitize LLM-extracted optional fields server-side. Never push without explicit user approval.

**Testing accounts:** José Carlos (+526565884840, America/Mexico_City), Oscar Perez (+526563954480, America/New_York).

**Legacy marketplace ("Handy"):** archived to `~/handy-legacy/`, do NOT reactivate without documented decision.

